games.comment: Mark Sanchez didn't have pretty stats - he was 14-of-22 for 163 yards and a touchdown - but he once again did a great job moving the chains and avoiding turnovers. Sanchez was at his best when it counted; he was 11-of-17 for 148 yards and the score in the second half. Sanchez nearly had a second touchdown twice;
Mark Sanchez the rest of the way, so I'll focus on the Eagles.
